)Attr
 @ type(input ) caps(off) hilite(uscore)
 $ type(input ) caps(on ) hilite(uscore)
 # type(text) hilite(reverse) color(turq)
)Body Expand(\\)
+-\-\#(z ISPF Git Interface - Connect/Clone)+-\-\
%Command ===>_zcmd
+
%Name:        @zigirep                         +
+
+
%Local Directory:   +? to browse omvs folder structure
 @localrep                                                                    +
+
+Notes:
+1. Don't use spaces in name field.
+2. Repository will be named (and stored) in USS as /localdirectory/name
+3. Fails if /localdirectory/name is present
+   Override with @A+ a Y
+4. Thirtytwo characters should be enough for a repo-name :)
+
                  +Press%Enter+to continue, or%F3+to cancel
)Init
 .help = zigihp1
)Proc
  ver (&zigirep,nb)
  ver (&localrep,nb)
)end
